# Deny by default. This image has two documented roles—Fram coordinator and
# North gateway—and neither needs the SDK workspace, transcripts, private docs,
# caches, tests, archived web apps, or provider/account state.
**

!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!LICENSE
!flake.lock

!bin/
bin/**
!bin/github-flake-input-pin

!out/
out/**
!out/north/
out/north/**
!out/north/gatepolicy.clj

!deploy/
deploy/**
!deploy/gateway/
deploy/gateway/**
!deploy/gateway/gateway.clj
